data.description: This split foyer home offers a desirable layout with 3 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, making it spacious and accommodating. The main living area boasts an inviting open floor plan, making it ideal for both everyday living and hosting guests. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and features a convenient island for added workspace and seating.  Reverse Osmosis water system conveys. The dining area provides ample space for a large dining table, making it perfect for meals and gatherings. The primary bedroom serves as a retreat, featuring two closets and an attached bathroom with dual vanity sinks, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. Two additional generously sized bedrooms on the main level offer flexibility for various needs such as guest rooms or home offices. The lower level features a spacious recreational room, providing plenty of room for leisure activities or extra living space. Additionally, a full bathroom and laundry room are located on this level, with the washer and dryer conveying with the property. Outside, the back deck offers a lovely space for outdoor entertaining or simply relaxing, surrounded by woods and nature. The oversized 2-car garage includes shelving units and ample space for a work area, providing convenient storage and functionality. The HOA includes road maintenance, snow removal, and access to a pond and park. Conveniently located just 20 minutes from Winchester & Strasburg, this home offers a blend of comfort, convenience, and modern amenities for comfortable living. Property being sold AS IS, WHERE IS. Sellers will not be making any repairs. Any inspections will be at buyers expense for informational purposes only.
